AITEX is involved in several international R&amp;D networks, platforms, etc.: TEXTRANET(Textile Transfer Network),GEDRT, CIRFS, European  Technological Textile Platform for the future of Textile-Clothing sector, European Platform for Sport Innovation (EPSI), Bio-based Consortium, EIP Raw Materials (through a committment), EUMAT(European Technology Platform for Advanced Engineering Materials and Technologies), Captechs of the European Defence Agency (EDA)&#xd;
&#xd;
AITEX places special emphasis on collaboration with the REDIT and FEDIT technology centres, as well as a wide variety of universities and research and technology centres nationally and internationally.&#xd;
AITEX is also part of international certifications networks including TEXTRANET, ÖKO-TEX, GEDRT, GOLF and AELAF.
